Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Einstein Discovery features:

Set Up Einstein Discovery
Get Started Using Einstein Discovery
Build Models in Einstein Discovery
Manage and Deploy Models in Einstein Discovery
About Models
Evaluate Model Quality

Model Evaluation includes Metrics for Numeric Use Cases, Metrics for Binary Classification Use Cases: Overview Tab, Model Evaluation Tab, Threshold Evaluation, Prediction Examination Tab.

Metrics also include Metrics for Multiclass Classification Use Cases.
Compare Models, Deploy Models, Manage Prediction Definitions and Models.

Predict & Improve Outcomes, Decision Optimization (Beta)

The R code contains transformations made to your CRM Analytics dataset and scoring code. It's available for Binary Classification models and is intended for model transparency only.
title: Setting Up and Using Einstein Discovery in Salesforce Analytics
